==In popular culture==

The Wong Tai Sin Fortune-telling and Oblation Arcade was a site of the Fast Forward in the seventh leg of the reality TV show &quot;The Amazing Race 2&quot;, in which racers had to find the fortune-teller Amelia Chow (in stall No.44) to have a face reading and a palm reading.

