*** Married Cewangduo&#x27;erji (策旺多爾濟; d. 1751) of the Aohan in January/February 1730

* Secondary consort, of the Tanggiya clan (側福晉 唐佳氏)Titles: Secondary Consort of the Crown Prince (皇太子侧妃), Secondary Consort of the Seventh Prince (七王子侧妃), &quot;Secondary Consort to Prince Limi of the First Rank&quot; (和碩亲王侧妃)
