==Family==
In 2000, scholar Cynthia Lawford published birth records implying that Landon had in fact borne children in the 1820s from a secret affair with William Jerdan. Details of Letitia&#x27;s children by Jerdan (Ella, Fred and Laura) and their descendants can be found in Susan Matoff.

